{"tid":1175913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度女將神車塗滿牛屎降溫","createTime":"2019-05-29T01:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T01:49:36.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"787fd88b0dac148346ee6d8f78e2cfbe61147e75","tid":1175913,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/y2o79wwv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fy2o79wwv&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2BZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=3f423466\" target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/y2o79wwv</a><br />\n<br />\nA Toyota Corolla has been covered in cow dung in an innovative effort to keep<br />\nthe vehicle cool in India's scorching summer.<br />\n <br />\n一輛神A創新的用牛屎覆蓋全車以利於在印度夏季裡保持涼爽<br />\n <br />\nThe Corolla Altis, owned by Sejalben Shah, was smeared in a neat layer of the<br />\nanimal waste, covering the whole bodywork in a bid to absorb heat.<br />\n <br />\n印女將牛便便塗抹一層在車體上用以隔熱<br />\n <br />\nCow dung is widely used throughout rural India to keep houses and huts cool<br />\nin the summer months and other hot spells.<br />\n <br />\n牛屎在印度農村被廣泛使用，以保持在夏季和其他炎熱天氣時房屋涼爽<br />\n <br />\nHowever, the smell of the car may prove problematic.<br />\n <br />\n然而，車的味道可能很珈哩<br />\n <br />\nRupesh Gauranga Das, who posted the pictures, said the bizarre new paint job<br />\nwas the 'best use of cow dung' he had ever seen.<br />\n <br />\n秀圖者說：&quot;這可能是他看過最佳的牛屎使用法了&quot;<br />\n <br />\nWeather forecasts for Ahmedabad, in the state of Gujarat, show temperatures<br />\nrising to more than 111F (44C) in the coming days.<br />\n <br />\n未來幾天氣溫將升至111F（44C）以上<br />\n <br />\nIn May 2016 the temperature in the city reached a record 118F (48C).<br />\n <br />\n2016年5月，該市的氣溫達到創紀錄的118F（48C）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kNTi8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3kNTi8.png&h=a9c5343f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8m8S4qP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8m8S4qP.png&h=d9eca1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8FxgMD9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8FxgMD9.png&h=84d54ace&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfR1XLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfR1XLQ.png&h=6d4e818e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7996ef2b090a05d31bfd259b290cb722ad516b57","tid":1175913,"uid":41368,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:09:46.000Z","msg":"又塗得幾靚喎"},{"pid":"fa8f5ed2ce342f3fb607a91c6866f0b6bd94f58b","tid":1175913,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:11:00.000Z","msg":"..."},{"pid":"885d4e7ffc8cb4f323139897b9535350618e646c","tid":1175913,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b0ae47cd903b5ae95eb8b3803f85460493b7ec","tid":1175913,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:12:00.000Z","msg":"無咩所謂啦<br />\n咪幾襯個國家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0626142eee54da87bdf029a25c17ae4108b0b637","tid":1175913,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:12:21.000Z","msg":"落雨點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54a0a63a525415cca7ddad3b49b368768cf3c8aa","tid":1175913,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0626142eee54da87bdf029a25c17ae4108b0b637","tid":1175913,"uid":224510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:12:21.000Z","msg":"落雨點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"變左痾爛屎"},{"pid":"3d040c8a276167a646771ccb0fdf1477e0b64f58","tid":1175913,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"